Title: Premasathi Coming Suun
Actors: Jitendra Joshi, Suhas Joshi, Adinath Kothare, Vijay Patkar
Plot: Premasathi Coming Suun is a 2014 Marathi comedy about Aditya (Adinath Kothare), a young man in his early twenties who's family is looking for a bride for him, and Antara (Neha Pendse), the prospective bride with a hidden agenda.
